    "causal_summary": "Packet 013 recommended Option B: stop warming the resident JavaScript BM25 index by default and use SQLite FTS5 as the lexical BM25 rank provider, but only with guardrails. The risk is not RRF itself; the risk is losing shared synonym expansion, stemming visibility, identifier fixtures, and tests that distinguish implementation detail from retrieval quality.",
